version_description: While there are several highly rated Chords submitted for this song, they are lacking in different areas. Some of them are incomplete (they say "repeat chorus" or "repeat verse") which I find annoying when I want to read the lyrics to sing as I play a new song. Others have the Chords in the wrong place, something that could cause difficulty for new players. There are also one, the highest rated one, that is an excellent tab, but the user that contributed used the wrong chords names despite the fact that he labeled them correctly when he writes how to play them at the beginning of the song. One example of this is the use of the name C/G instead of Cadd9. My upload is complete, and I believe it has proper chord placement and proper chord names. If it is not accepted I know that I and several people I know would rather just use a copy of this rather than the current uploads on Ultimate Guitar.

version_description: The intro solo is accurate to the studio version of the song. The chord fingerings are accurate, as is the chord placement. I left out the backing vocals in the outro to make it more clear. I spruced up the tab formatting as requested. Specific differences from Version 1 include the C/G chord has been corrected to a Cadd9, and the solo has been corrected. Also, the fingering for every chord except the Cadd9 were fixed.
